@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Our Service";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
    <h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <p>
        Welcome to Vegetable Shopping Cart, your one-stop destination for all your vegetable shopping needs! Our platform is designed to provide you with a seamless and convenient shopping experience, allowing you to browse, select, and purchase fresh and high-quality vegetables from the comfort of your home.

        <h4>Our Mission</h4>

        At Vegetable Shopping Cart, we are committed to promoting healthy living by offering a wide variety of farm-fresh vegetables sourced directly from local farmers and trusted suppliers. We aim to make it easier for you to incorporate nutritious and delicious vegetables into your daily diet while supporting sustainable farming practices.

        <h4>What We Offer</h4>

        - Fresh Selection: We handpick the freshest vegetables to ensure you receive the best quality produce.
        - Convenience: Skip the hassle of grocery store crowds and long lines by shopping online at your convenience.
        - Variety: Explore a diverse range of vegetables, from staples like carrots and spinach to exotic finds like bok choy and kale.
        - Quality Assurance: We prioritize quality and freshness in every product we offer, guaranteeing your satisfaction with every purchase.
        - Customer Satisfaction: Your satisfaction is our top priority. We strive to provide excellent customer service and a seamless shopping experience from start to finish.

        <h4>How It Works</h4>

        1. Browse: Explore our extensive selection of fresh vegetables.
        2. Add to Cart: Select the items you want to purchase and add them to your cart.
        3. Checkout: Review your order, choose your preferred payment method, and complete your purchase.
        4. Delivery: Sit back and relax as we deliver your order straight to your doorstep.

        <h4>Get in Touch</h4>

        Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Feel free to reach out to our customer support team for assistance or inquiries.

        Thank you for choosing Vegetable Shopping Cart for all your vegetable needs. Happy shopping!
    </p>
</main>